Colombia to Offer Colcap ETF Within Three Months, Cordoba Says

-- B y   B l a k e   S c h m i d t
-- 
2011-05-17T15:49:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-17/colombia-to-offer-colcap-etf-within-three-months-cordoba-says.html
Colombia’s bourse seeks to offer its
first exchange-traded fund within three months in an alliance
with  Blackrock Inc. (BLK) , said Juan Pablo Cordoba, President of  Bolsa
de Valores de Colombia. (BVC)   The fund would follow Colombia’s Colcap Index and is
pending approval from the country’s regulatory agency, Cordoba
said in a presentation in Bogota with Miguel Angel Zapatero,
director of iShares sales for Blackrock in Chile.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Blake Schmidt in Bogota 
 bschmidt16@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
